 />\n初3復出，番工冇時間睇錦多場。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同埋寫馬經都係主力一場分析"},{"pid":"267c7fd55483ddea9a7787ac0023f67116666138","tid":84873,"uid":42101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T06:59:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80f9af6049b78f8ecba33c0a01d068cb12046247","tid":84873,"uid":42101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T07:33:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3dd4a0dd47ca4938f3327a7a116e9855fc05bf8","tid":84873,"uid":42101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T09:05:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80db63c35f87f66873a90075cd8eac7526aaa9dd","tid":84873,"uid":47135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T09:08:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d550a5ecb7ced824e422c120466e45a9b8c6d565","tid":84873,"uid":44678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T09:38:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e38550f4c024e98fc0d8cc091f989a0a2f05d86","tid":84873,"uid":42101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T10:10:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4be3e783a04659bce2b96d5a9c673c20f5c3b36f","tid":84873,"uid":60807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T10:15:45.000Z","msg":"唔知點解我都鐘意五星特工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n位置可以嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c23daa1a250a0d922e65c863894d2f1c3f509806","tid":84873,"uid":42101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T10:21:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知點解我都鐘意五星特工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n位置可以嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n分析講過佢有賠會去 贏唔贏要睇主要對手 大將風雲。 我覺5星有分在手，後泥腳，希望係泥地習慣，有主騎試泥有追勢但要騎。靠田泰安點樣騎。5星受硬功夫，受邊多過用薑繩。"},{"pid":"9f65f2adf53ac6c5fa3c3fd50926b0ca2cf8ff35","tid":84873,"uid":42101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T10:23:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔知點解我都鐘意五星特工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n位置可以嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n分析講過佢有賠會去 贏唔贏要睇主要對手 大將風雲。 我覺5星有分在手，後泥腳，希望係泥地習慣，有主騎試泥有追勢但要騎。靠田泰安點樣騎。5星受硬功夫，受邊多過用薑繩。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇賠去馬得e場，落班冇水食，加上此馬不是4，5班馬，蔡john無理由要隻馬浪費時間"},{"pid":"be392e7c563664442317df6931e0a103e84eb671","tid":84873,"uid":42101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T10:25:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔知點解我都鐘意五星特工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n位置可以嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n分析講過佢有賠會去 贏唔贏要睇主要對手 大將風雲。 我覺5星有分在手，後泥腳，希望係泥地習慣，有主騎試泥有追勢但要騎。靠田泰安點樣騎。5星受硬功夫，受邊多過用薑繩。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇賠去馬得e場，落班冇水食，加上此馬不是4，5班馬，蔡john無理由要隻馬浪費時間</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個人睇同場冇隻穩，有禮冇水食又傷又欠課，同場初跑泥大把連泥閘都冇個，新馬又多，冇對手點解唔去？等多對手浪費體力？"},{"pid":"1f039b004f886e2cab9311fb8b17d71a8b113b04","tid":84873,"uid":1373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T10:26:03.000Z","msg":"後追唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd605578d0c47668dcff8ad4114e971304538374","tid":84873,"uid":42101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T10:27:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>後追唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n5星特工有前速可以放前少少，第4場隻隻放。5星守2行2疊，3行2疊都夠追啦。"}]}